{"tid":1698830,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【割蓆割到地裂】懷疑大公報、通視影片上載時間有問題既入黎","createTime":"2019-11-07T19:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T07:34:06.000Z","uid":272825,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e85cc22f7edd13bf881c05a87e2e61f54e1c9f23","tid":1698830,"uid":272825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T19:03:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">先聲明，<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span>！</span><br />\n<br />\n我都好明白大家覺得何妖自編自導自演，<br />\n好多野都好巧合，同埋好令人懷疑......<br />\n但我又覺得繼續落去，會對位手足好唔公平。<br />\n人地冒死去抗爭，我地呢？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">割蓆割到地裂？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">【有關YOUTUBE 段片的時間顯示問題】</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我唔係ＩＴ人，但我都知其實要check 一段YOUTUBE既真正upload 時間好簡單，<br />\nＧＯＯＧＬＥ大神有海量教學...<br />\n可以參考:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2YS7YWnoYwo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2YS7YWnoYwo&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK%2BBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=af9ea124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2YS7YWnoYwo</a><br />\n<br />\n唔想睇既，可以直接按以下連結:<br />\n<a href=\"https://citizenevidence.amnestyusa.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcitizenevidence.amnestyusa.org%2F&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK%2BBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=fd477f2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://citizenevidence.amnestyusa.org/</a><br />\n<br />\n然後再copy and paste 返d影片既link 落去，就搵到佢「actual upload time」<br />\n(要注意，需要要查到既時間+8 個鐘，點解? 注意time zone 呀大佬)<br />\n<br />\n經測試後：<br />\n【通屎影片】何君堯遇襲送院 在醫院報平安<br />\n（<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BBpgLo6lAvU&amp;t=5s）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBBpgLo6lAvU%26t%3D5s%EF%BC%89&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK%2BBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=63184d4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BBpgLo6lAvU&amp;t=5s）</a><br />\nVideo ID: BBpgLo6lAvU<br />\nUpload Date (YYYY/MM/DD): 2019-11-06<br />\nUpload Time (UTC): 04:00:48 (convert to local time of Hong Kong = 12:00)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">【FACEBOOK 段片的時間顯示問題】</span></span><br />\n<br />\n至於FACEBOOK 就煩少少，要CHECK 佢既TIMESTAMP，<br />\n但我唔係好識睇D 代碼，唔係好搵到個TIMESTAMP 代碼....<br />\n不過....其實呢個POST可能只係系統問題，因為如果直接係大公報FACEBOOK 瀏覽個POST，個時間就去左11月5日....<br />\n但係，<br />\n如果你COPY THE POST LINK <br />\n然後再睇個時間呢...就會「正常」返，變返11月6日上年11:54<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xUzVvOr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxUzVvOr.png&h=afcf44c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n=============================================<br />\n點解會出現時間誤差？<br />\n太多原因，我唔SURE。但估計同VPN 或 PRE-UPLOAD + EDITTED 或TIME ZONE 有關，<br />\n希望有高手解答。"},{"pid":"150533d6c1faed0e363cf1d3140174896c499f6d","tid":1698830,"uid":272825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T19:03:24.000Z","msg":"自推5次訓覺"},{"pid":"d47128be7d261029dc3ebaada2a4848aae0e377f","tid":1698830,"uid":272825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T19:03:36.000Z","msg":"自推4次訓覺"},{"pid":"08ed546d70b878a1a960066bf731d5f9ce05529b","tid":1698830,"uid":272825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T19:03:46.000Z","msg":"自推3次訓覺"},{"pid":"4e20dc0c333fd6774416cfe7cdb8de2d9a370a2a","tid":1698830,"uid":272825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T19:03:56.000Z","msg":"自推2次訓覺"},{"pid":"82fa7012250de8af5214f9f626d7b2c5cf55bd2a","tid":1698830,"uid":272825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T19:04:07.000Z","msg":"自推最後一次，真係訓覺 88"},{"pid":"61ca6a8a324ac87e12896398215da893261aeb06","tid":1698830,"uid":150129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T19:04:25.000Z","msg":"有心人 幫樓主推"},{"pid":"3b74d7a96236c0c902a8146a5e3c262a6d208d81","tid":1698830,"uid":24097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T19:07:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91f12972d10dc05dc9778c879da2b0681178e286","tid":1698830,"uid":272825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T19:09:45.000Z","msg":"BTW，點解「TIMESTAMP」可以證明一段影片的ACTUAL UPLOAD TIME?<br />\n同埋TIME ZONE 點影響FACEBOOK 既時間顯示？<br />\n<br />\n自己睇大神解釋:<br />\n原文：<a href=\"https://www.metabunk.org/how-to-find-the-exact-upload-time-of-a-facebook-photo.t4367/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.metabunk.org%2Fhow-to-find-the-exact-upload-time-of-a-facebook-photo.t4367%2F&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK%2BBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=76e44bd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.metabunk.org/how-to-find-the-exact-upload-time-of-a-facebook-photo.t4367/</a><br />\n<br />\n重點：Timestamps in Facebook use &quot;Unix epoch&quot; format, and you can convert this to actual time with online calculators, like <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.epochconverter.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochconverter.com%2F&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK%2BBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=4240b186\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.epochconverter.com/</a>"},{"pid":"33a87118a99dc67bcb11353e3e2e1c4977667ffc","tid":1698830,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T19:09:47.000Z","msg":"呢d真相post 無人會推"},{"pid":"3738b76ad859898528fa3006c59912009b7bc8f3","tid":1698830,"uid":272825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33a87118a99dc67bcb11353e3e2e1c4977667ffc","tid":1698830,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T19:09:47.000Z","msg":"呢d真相post 無人會推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T19:10:19.000Z","msg":"有你就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我真係訓緊..."},{"pid":"551e6abd7cf77a8f220c386da38ec90fa714d830","tid":1698830,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T19:20:57.000Z","msg":"跟本大把人仲有鋪割蓆癮<br />\n總之覺得影響到自己既野，割<br />\n如果學到藍屍咁團結<br />\n香港 贏撚硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b6ab6be14129bbc5f9e5b87c2a26b73657425f","tid":1698830,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T07:31:25.000Z","msg":"唔明。。。<br />\n<br />\n樓主整個總結好冇"},{"pid":"6136d7a7ff542c5cd230e288cfcce347b9511271","tid":1698830,"uid":331192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T07:34:06.000Z","msg":"唔係好識 但推左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}